  <brief_title>EndoCuff-assisted Versus Standard Colonoscopy for Adenoma Detection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study to Compare EndoCuff-assisted With Standard Colonoscopy for the Detection of Adenomas</official_title>
  <sponsors>
